Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.70,0:22:51.17,ED2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be2}騙子  膽小鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.25,0:22:54.18,ED2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be2}這樣的我
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.27,0:22:59.82,ED2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be2}只能在夢中綻放
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.94,0:23:02.60,ED2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be2}躲進月光的影子
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.69,0:23:05.22,ED2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be2}我真的哭了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.43,0:23:08.04,ED2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be2}但卻沒法流淚
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.24,0:23:11.08,ED2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be2}因為我的眼淚已經枯竭
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.19,0:23:13.84,ED2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be2}如果能原諒一切的話
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.92,0:23:17.50,ED2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be2}或許能再流淚
